$ PowerShell statement: using …

There are three `using` variants in → Windows/PowerShell:
  • → Windows/PowerShell/language/statement/using/assembly[`using assembly`]
  • → Windows/PowerShell/language/statement/using/namespace[`using namespace`]
  • → Windows/PowerShell/language/statement/using/module[`using module`]

A `using` → Windows/PowerShell/language/statement[statement] must appear before any other statements in a → Windows/PowerShell/script[script].
